<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Cancelled - TechTrainers</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #292524;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fafaf9;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        
        .appointment-card {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .appointment-detail {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #fecaca;
        }
        
        .appointment-detail:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #991b1b;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .cancellation-info {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .cancellation-info h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: #d97706;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #6b7280;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #292524;
            color: #a8a29e;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #d97706;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: #e2e8f0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .cancelled-badge {
            background: #fef2f2;
            color: #dc2626;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .refund-info {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .refund-info h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #166534;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .btn {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚ùå Appointment Cancelled</h1>
            <p>Your training session has been cancelled</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p>We're writing to confirm that your appointment has been cancelled as requested. We're sorry to see you go, but we understand that plans can change.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                <span class="cancelled-badge">‚úó Cancelled</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="appointment-card">
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üìÖ Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">‚è∞ Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentTime}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üí™ Session Type:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{sessionType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üèãÔ∏è Trainer:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{trainerName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üè∑Ô∏è Booking ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{bookingId}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cancellation-info">
                <h3>üìã Cancellation Details</h3>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Cancelled by:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{cancelledBy}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Cancellation time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{cancellationTime}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if cancellationReason}}
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Reason:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{cancellationReason}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            {{#if refundAmount}}
            <div class="refund-info">
                <h3>üí∞ Refund Information</h3>
                <p>Your refund of <strong>${{refundAmount}}</strong> has been processed and will appear in your account within 5-7 business days.</p>
                <p><strong>Refund method:</strong> {{refundMethod}}</p>
                <p><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> {{refundTransactionId}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="{{bookNewAppointmentUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">üìÖ Book New Appointment</a>
                <a href="{{viewAvailableTrainersUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">üë• View Trainers</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p><strong>üéØ Don't Let This Stop Your Progress!</strong></p>
            <p>We understand that life happens, but we don't want this to derail your fitness journey. Our team is here to help you get back on track whenever you're ready.</p>
            
            <p><strong>üìû Need Help Rescheduling?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Browse available trainers and time slots</li>
                <li>Contact our support team for personalized assistance</li>
                <li>Set up recurring appointments to maintain consistency</li>
                <li>Consider virtual training sessions for flexibility</li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p>If you have any questions about this cancellation or need help booking a new appointment, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> or visit our <a href="{{supportUrl}}">Support Center</a>.</p>
            
            <p>We hope to see you back soon!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>The TechTrainers Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                <strong>TechTrainers</strong> - Empowering Fitness Through Technology<br>
                <a href="{{companyWebsite}}">{{companyWebsite}}</a> | 
                <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a><br>
                <a href="{{bookNewAppointmentUrl}}">Book Again</a> | 
                <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>